      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "yeah ideally you'd somehow be able to tell it just that in this region there are 32 identical slices and that they're instances for the 32-wide datapath around it, and that it has to figure out PnR inside, outside, and has to figure out how it likes the ports placed.\n\nI'd probably give it opportunity to just place the ports wherever on the grid on one side in teh small slice and just roll with what it likes best there.",
